title: Utley's takeout slide breaks Tejada's leg in Game 2 of NLDS
text:
> Top News Utley's takeout slide breaks Tejada's leg in Game 2 of NLDS Los Angeles Dodgers' Enrique Hernandez, left, steals second past New York Mets shortstop Ruben Tejada during the seventh inning in Game 2 of baseball's National League Division Series, Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 in Los Angeles.
